# SQLite WAL / shared-memory files (transient; only the main *.db is tracked).
# The causal KB at build_agent/learning/causal_kb.db lives in git; its
# -wal and -shm sidecars must NOT be committed. wal_checkpoint(FULL) at
# the end of each harness run consolidates everything into the main file.
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
*.db-journal